data.description: Introducing a charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Hemet, CA. This property is sold AS IS, offering an excellent opportunity for customization and personalization. The highlight of this home is the inviting pool and separate jacuzzi, perfect for relaxation and entertaining. The pool system is brand new, ensuring optimal functionality and enjoyment. The spacious back yard provides ample room for outdoor activities and gatherings. Inside, a new AC unit keeps the home comfortably cool. Situated on a corner lot, this home offers added privacy and a sense of space. Conveniently located near restaurants, you'll enjoy easy access to dining options. The kitchen features elegant granite countertops, adding a touch of sophistication to your culinary experiences. Embrace the potential and make this Hemet home your own. *** Seller is offering to PAY BUYERS 2-1 BUYDOWN or Closing Costs up to the same value ***
